1 Woodland, Willie Mae Powell, Roberta Brown (Odell), Susie Green, Evelyn Green, Brenda
2 Allen, and Lillian Green; cousin, J.C. Green; and a host of nieces, nephews, godchildren,
3 relatives, and friends; he will be deeply missed, but the legacy of his love and service shall
4 live on in perpetuity in the hearts and minds of those who were privileged to have known
5 him.
6 THEREFORE, BE IT RESOLVED that the Legislature of Louisiana does hereby
7 express heartfelt condolences on the death of Dr. Joe S. Green, "The Bayou Bishop"; does
8 hereby extend enduring appreciation for his military service and service to Rapides Parish;
9 and does hereby extend sincere wishes that his family, friends, and loved ones find comfort
10 in their shared memories of his beautiful life.
